# CSLv3-native fixture — covers §, modals, evidence marks, dense math, indent scopes.
# See CSLv3/specs/12_TOKENIZER + 13_GRAMMAR_SELF for the authoritative grammar.

§ sphere_sdf ≡ @differentiable ⊗ @lipschitz<1.0>
  I> length(p) - r
  W! p ∈ vec3
  W! r ∈ f32'pos
  → f32
  ✓ O(1) normal via bwd_diff
  ✓ Lipschitz-1 by construction

§ render_scene ≡ @staged
  W! target ∈ {GPU, NoAlloc, Deadline<16ms>}
  I> grid(cam.size) ▷ parallel
    x ∈ 0..cam.width
    y ∈ 0..cam.height
  → Image

§ effect Physics<World>
  W! step ∈ (f32 → World)
  W! contact ∈ (Entity ⊗ Entity → Option<Hit>)
  ‼ conservation : mass + momentum invariant

§ invariants
  W! ∀ SDF'L<k ≤ 1> ∃ bwd_diff(SDF) computing O(1) normal
  W! ∀ ray_march loop terminating in O(max_t / eps) iterations
  ◐ higher-order Jet<T, ∞> lazy stream TODO
  ○ inverse-rendering stdlib FIXME

∎
